"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/91374","HM Treasury","false","2014-09-23","<p>Since January 2011, central Government Departments have been required to publish on Contracts Finder information on the tenders issued and contracts they award with a value over £10,000</p><p><a href="http://www.gov.uk/contracts-finder" target="_blank">www.gov.uk/contracts-finder</a></p><p> </p><p> </p><p>In addition, Departments including HM Treasury routinely publish details of transactions over £25,000 <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/25000-spend" target="_blank">https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/25000-spend</a></p>","South Northamptonshire","Andrea Leadsom","209072","2014-09-23T11:59:38.430137Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/91374/answer","Biography information for Andrea Leadsom","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/91374/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/91374/answer",,,,,,,,"14","Treasury","CaTreasury","2014-09-10","Barclays","1","House of Commons","To ask Mr Chancellor of the Exchequer, what (a) goods and (b) services are provided by Barclays Bank to his Department; what the purpose of each such good or service is; how much his Department paid for each such good or service; and if he will make a statement.","false","Biography information for Sir David Amess","Southend West","Mr David Amess","209071"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/91375","HM Treasury","false","2014-09-23","<p>Since January 2011, central Government Departments have been required to publish on Contracts Finder information on the tenders issued and contracts they award with a value over £10,000</p><p><a href="http://www.gov.uk/contracts-finder" target="_blank">www.gov.uk/contracts-finder</a></p><p> </p><p> </p><p>In addition, Departments including HM Treasury routinely publish details of transactions over £25,000 <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/25000-spend" target="_blank">https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/25000-spend</a></p>","South Northamptonshire","Andrea Leadsom","209071","2014-09-23T11:59:38.5239009Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/91375/answer","Biography information for Andrea Leadsom","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/91375/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/91375/answer",,,,,,,,"14","Treasury","CaTreasury","2014-09-10","Barclays","1","House of Commons","To ask Mr Chancellor of the Exchequer, what contracts his Department has signed with Barclays Bank in each month since July 2010; what each such contract is for; how much his Department paid for each such contract; how many such contracts (a) have expired, (b) have been terminated and (c) are current; and if he will make a statement.","false","Biography information for Sir David Amess","Southend West","Mr David Amess","209072"
