also not possible to quantify the potential impact on gilt rates had additional debt been source by the exchequer.</p>","Devizes","Claire Perry","208958 ; 208959 ; 208961 ; 208962","2014-10-14T11:45:34.9934224Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/91552/answer","Biography information for Claire Perry","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/91552/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/91552/answer",,,,,,,,"27","Transport","Transport","2014-09-10","Network Rail","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Transport, what estimate he has made of the additional annual cost to Network Rail of borrowing from private financial markets rather than the Government in control periods 3, 4 and 5.","false","Biography information for Kelvin Hopkins","Luton North","Kelvin Hopkins","208960"
