also not possible to quantify the potential impact on gilt rates had additional debt been source by the exchequer.</p>","Devizes","Claire Perry","208958 ; 208959 ; 208960 ; 208962","2014-10-14T11:45:35.0715602Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/91553/answer","Biography information for Claire Perry","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/91553/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/91553/answer",,,,,,,,"27","Transport","Transport","2014-09-10","Network Rail","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Transport, what interest rate was applied to Network Rail's borrowing from the markets in each year of control periods 3, 4 and 5.","false","Biography information for Kelvin Hopkins","Luton North","Kelvin Hopkins","208961"
